Class Bounds3D

java.lang.Object
org.ivoa.dm.measurement.Uncertainty
org.ivoa.dm.measurement.Bounds3D
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
@Embeddable @VoDml(id="meas:Bounds3D", role=dataType) public class Bounds3D extends Uncertainty implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations
Provide the edges of a 3D uncertainty space. Rather than being relative to the associated Coordinate, these represent ranges along each axis of that Coordinate space. dataType: Bounds3D
